long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Adds new data columns for Team Fortress 2 match analysis in logs.tf

Currently 2 extra columns are shown:
- DA%: Damage dealt by player over the total damage of the match.
- DE: Damage efficiency. Damage dealt (DA) over Damage Taken (DT)

** I'm not related in any way to logs.tf site **
